    "description": "<div>&nbsp;Hey <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vNDk5ODQ3Mjg_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--bb3b2f1cc2dea2dbeb374c74241d4fcd7eac5ae9\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"49984728\" alt=\"Mubeen Dildar-Mia\" title=\"Mubeen Dildar-Mia, Head SEO Coordinator at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBNi0+gI=--17c301bfdb3ad779c8a5bd6896eb76d427bb6e25/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Mubeen\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment>, <br><br>I have found a few issues with this client, and Clayton wanted me to list them out to you here so they are on your radar, and hash them out with the right people to get these things addressed.<br><br>I am listing the things I have found so far through our GBP audits, and after digging into why the client is stating Charlotte GBP has been pending verification for over 3 weeks now. (<em>Which I think will more than likely turn into a suspension due to missing local signals and such</em>)</div><h1>Issues found so far:</h1><div>\n<br><strong>Charlotte GBP -</strong><br>- Currently using the homepage is currently only optimized for AZ not NC<br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 248, 226);\">FIXED </span>- Updated GBP to use Charlotte lander<br>- no hours listed<br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 248, 226);\">FIXED </span>- Added 7:30am to 5pm as site states<br>- Mooresville GBP has Charlotte listed in it's service area<br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 248, 226);\">FIXED </span>- removed from Mooresville service areas and added to Charlotte<br><br><strong>Footer -</strong><br>Not all locations NAPW exist in footer<br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 240, 219);\">Task Created to Implement this</span> - <a href=\"https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/46000874/todos/9619799392\">Footer Updates - J404 ASAP Commercial Doors </a><br><br><strong>Phoenix Lander -</strong><br>Another page exists for this location, but the GBP is currently using - <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"autolinked\" data-behavior=\"truncate\" href=\"https://asapcommercialdoors.com/service-areas/phoenix-az-2/\">https://asapcommercialdoors.com/service-areas/phoenix-az-2/</a><br>The other page is <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"autolinked\" data-behavior=\"truncate\" href=\"https://asapcommercialdoors.com/service-areas/phoenix-az/\">https://asapcommercialdoors.com/service-areas/phoenix-az/</a><br><br><strong>Location Pages - </strong><br>Location pages do not contain any local signals of NAPW and map embeds on them<br>&nbsp;</div>",
