    "description": "<div>Hey <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vMzUyODgyOTU_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--3787eaa7f4cca720cfc3a740cd4aae25aba0cf94\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"35288295\" alt=\"Fed\" title=\"Fed, Vice President at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBOd0GgI=--7a551fa3a5cd33b2948d9031de3c568485866302/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Fed\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment>,<br><br>We have another situation here: we need to figure out the GBP phone numbers to ensure NAPW consistency as we improve the site's footer structure to add all locations and set up citations.<br><br> The site lists only two locations in the footer, both with phone numbers that are not associated with their GBPs, so not sure what these are either.<br> <br><br><strong>Can you please communicate with the appropriate contact:</strong><br>- Confirm if the current phone numbers on each GBP are their respective unique local numbers.<br>- If not, get us a list of the correct local numbers to use for NAPW consistency across GBP (<em>secondary if GBP tracking exists</em>), site NAP in footer and respective location pages, Citations.<br><br>To not further delay the footer updates, as these are critical SEO elements that need to be addressed ASAP, we will <strong>proceed with using each of the GBPs' primary phone numbers in the site footer</strong>. But we can change this if needs be once the client gets back to us.<br><br> <strong>Phoenix</strong> <br>Number on Site in Footer - (833) 373-8761<br>GBP Primary - (833) 299-3888 <br>GBP Secondary - n/a <br><br> <strong>Mooresville </strong><br>Number on Site in Footer -&nbsp; (980) 351-9710 <br>GBP Primary - (980) 294-0324<br>GBP Secondary -&nbsp; n/a <br><br><strong>Gilbert AZ<br></strong>Number on Site in Footer - n/a<br>GBP Primary - (480) 442-8918<br>GBP Secondary -&nbsp; n/a <br><br><strong>Charlotte </strong><br>Number on Site in Footer - n/a&nbsp;<br>GBP Primary - (980) 202-3660&nbsp;<br>GBP Secondary -&nbsp; n/a&nbsp;</div>",
